headline: 2 Dividend Stocks to Double Up on Right Now
summary: Real estate investment trusts, or REITs, are largely trading at low valuations because of the interest-rate environment.  Despite the beaten-down share prices, many REITs' businesses are doing extremely well.  Two to take a closer look at right now are Realty Income and Prologis.
